show.description: When a humble village man returns as the powerful CEO of a billion-dollar company, his truth is questioned, his family turns against him, and a web of lies threatens to destroy everything he built. But with honor, love, and a secret weapon, he must fight to reclaim his dignity and reveal who the real imposter is.
